Package edu.cnm.deepdive.videopoker.model

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Card
    This class represents a playing card in a deck or a hand.
    Converter
    This class exists to convert a String sequence into the rules for a poker hand.
    Deck
    This class represents a deck of card objects.
    Game
    This class contains information for the state of the game being currently played.
    PlayerHand
    This class represents the hand actually being played in a game of poker, as opposed to the poker hand type with corresponding rules and worth.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Rank
    This class represents the rank value of a playing card.
    Suit
    This class represents the suit value in the order Clubs, Diamonds, Hearts, Spades.
    Suit.Color
    A store of the color state of the suit in BLACK or RED.
